queries.name: imdb_dataset.discover-tables-find-tables-and-row-counts
queries.sql:
SELECT table_name 
FROM information_schema.tables
WHERE (table_name like '%')

queries.name: imdb_dataset.discover-tables-column-metadata-for-distribution_types
queries.sql:
SELECT column_name, lower(data_type) as data_type, is_nullable 
FROM information_schema.columns 
WHERE (table_name) = 'distribution_types'
ORDER BY ORDINAL_POSITION
